# **Azure Bicep & DevOps Portfolio**

Welcome to my **Cloud DevOps Portfolio**, showcasing my expertise in **Azure Bicep, Infrastructure as Code (IaC), CI/CD pipelines, and automation**.

---

## **📌 Projects Overview**
This portfolio highlights real-world Azure DevOps projects demonstrating **scalable, secure, and automated infrastructure provisioning**.

### **1️⃣ Azure Bicep CI/CD Pipeline**  
🚀 Automates **Azure infrastructure deployment** using **Azure Bicep** with **Azure DevOps & GitHub Actions**.  
📂 **Project:** Deploys **App Service, Key Vault, App Insights, and SQL Database** with a full CI/CD pipeline.  
📖 **Guide:** [Bicep CI/CD Documentation](docs/bicep-ci-cd.md)

### **2️⃣ Infrastructure Automation & Security with Azure Bicep**  
🏗 Deploys **secure, scalable Azure infrastructure** using **Bicep** with **automated security policies**.  
📂 **Project:** Implements **RBAC, network security, managed identities, and monitoring**.  
📖 **Guide:** [Azure Security Best Practices](docs/azure-security.md)

### **3️⃣ Operations Automation & Monitoring**  
🔧 Automates **system patching, middleware updates, and monitoring** using **PowerShell, DSC & Azure Bicep**.  
�� **Project:** Integrates **Application Insights, Azure Monitor, and automated alerts**.  
📖 **Guide:** [Operations Automation](docs/operations-automation.md)

