## **🛠 CI/CD Pipelines & Automation**
This portfolio integrates **CI/CD pipelines** using **Azure DevOps & GitHub Actions**.

📜 **CI/CD Pipelines:**  
- **Azure DevOps Pipeline for Bicep & PowerShell**: [`.azuredevops/pipeline.yml`](.azuredevops/pipeline.yml)  
- **GitHub Actions for Bicep Deployments**: [`.github/workflows/bicep-ci.yml`](.github/workflows/bicep-ci.yml)  
- **Infrastructure Testing & Compliance Checks** with **Checkov & Azure Policy**.  

